resisted british attempts at extradition kane was serving 18 years 
for ira activities after conviction on the evidence of an informer 
christopher black 
when the convictions resulting from blacks testimony were 
quashed after the maze breakout kane claimed he had been wrongly 
imprisoned but he still faced the escape charge 
he was one of 38 men who fled the maze on sept 25 1983 a 
