nominated as undersecretary of interior bracken is the board 
chairman of ballincon glass packaging corp in muncie 
martin l allday of midland texas will be nominated as the 
departments solicitor allday has been an attorney in private 
practice in midland since 1959 and a specialist in oil gas and 
minerals law 
