observers see a sale of the carrier as a facesaving device for 
unions that have locked themselves in a seething battle they have 
has focused almost entirely on the perceived evils of one man 
frank lorenzo chairman of eastern parent texas air corp 
of recent labor disputes i cant think of any that is so 
personalized and that onedimensional perspective is wrong 
tiffany said 
