alleged scheme about a week before he was fired demanded the 
practice be stopped and insisted it be reported to board of trade 
officials 
zechman said merrill lynch refused his requests and fired him on 
what he said were trumpedup charges 
zechman seeks 10 million in punitive damages and 10 million in 
actual damages from the defendants 
